9561,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3402","Title":"芜湖"},{"Id":"5a1a3b369a164ad7bde2a78ebb102951","Latitude":32.064735,"Longitude":118.802891,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3201","Title":"南京"},{"Id":"8be621cf04ab46c4901682345c7307c3","Latitude":30.280059,"Longitude":120.161693,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3301","Title":"杭州"},{"Id":"772a831d587c4335ac615d0a3e883d9e","Latitude":28.968047,"Longitude":117.135438,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN360281","Title":"乐平"}]}],"Markers":[{"Latitude":30.750912,"Longitude":120.762045,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3304","Title":"嘉兴 (出生地)","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e04a8f4becdf4086977b85a91755e888\");'><span id='e04a8f4becdf4086977b85a91755e888_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1120&endYear=1137')\">1120-1137年</a>，0-17岁</div><div id='e04a8f4becdf4086977b85a91755e888' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1120&endYear=1120')\">1120年</a>，出生。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1121&endYear=1127')\">1121-1127年</a>，随父居秀州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1128&endYear=1128')\">1128年</a>，是年秦国公薨，忠宣公奔丧归鄱阳，寓家秀州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1129&endYear=1129')\">1129年</a>，仍寓家秀州。从师业文，不以岁时寒暑辍。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1130&endYear=1130')\">1130年</a>，金人陷秀州，公兄弟奉秦国夫人、魏国夫人避乱归鄱阳，旋复还秀州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1131&endYear=1131')\">1131年</a>，诏下秀州，存问家属。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1132&endYear=1133')\">1132-1133年</a>，居秀州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1134&endYear=1134')\">1134年</a>，以父荫补承务郎。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1135&endYear=1137')\">1135-1137年</a>，居秀州。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.496704,"Longitude":120.318954,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3202","Title":"无锡","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"886724a4e23a4fbaa20186928dfd05f4\");'><span id='886724a4e23a4fbaa20186928dfd05f4_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1138&endYear=1141')\">1138-1141年</a>，18-21岁</div><div id='886724a4e23a4fbaa20186928dfd05f4' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1138&endYear=1138')\">1138年11月23日</a>，魏国夫人沈氏薨，孺慕攀号以孝闻。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1139&endYear=1139')\">1139年11月</a>，葬魏国夫人于无锡县。公兄弟即僧舍肄词业。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1140&endYear=1141')\">1140-1141年</a>，居家。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.280059,"Longitude":120.161693,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3301","Title":"杭州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"46ddf8b4966b4449a3bb56ec81f38b59\");'><span id='46ddf8b4966b4449a3bb56ec81f38b59_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1142&endYear=1143')\">1142-1143年</a>，22-23岁</div><div id='46ddf8b4966b4449a3bb56ec81f38b59' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1142&endYear=1142')\">1142年2月</a>，与兄适同试博学宏词科中选。名在第一。试题有《代枢密使谢赐玉带表》、《克敌弓铭》、《皇叔庆远军承宣使授昭化军节度使封安定郡王同知大宗正事制》、《唐勤政务本楼记》、《周成王搜岐阳颂》、《汉五家要说章句》。<span class='label'>作品：</span>《代枢密使谢赐玉带表》、《克敌弓铭》、《皇叔庆远军承宣使授昭化军节度使封安定郡王同知大宗正事制》、《唐勤政务本楼记》、《周成王搜岐阳颂》、《汉五家要说章句》。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-422页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1143&endYear=1143')\">1143年</a>，官秘书省正字。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"2475427b6d624040a7f9e93d058ccef2\");'><span id='2475427b6d624040a7f9e93d058ccef2_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1155&endYear=1160')\">1155-1160年</a>，35-40岁</div><div id='2475427b6d624040a7f9e93d058ccef2' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1155&endYear=1155')\">1155年</a>，入为秘书省正字。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1155&endYear=1155')\">1155年8月</a>，兼权直学士院。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1155&endYear=1155')\">1155年11月</a>，自秘书省正字兼权中书舍人以丁忧去国。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1155&endYear=1155')\">1155年</a>，官正字时有乞塞侥幸劄子、奏请复建鸿胪官劄子、乞禁奏祥瑞劄子。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞塞侥幸劄子、奏请复建鸿胪官劄子、乞禁奏祥瑞劄子。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-442页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1156&endYear=1156')\">1156年11月</a>，葬忠宣公于鄱阳。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1157&endYear=1157')\">1157年</a>，丁忧。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1158')\">1158年</a>，服阕，与弟迈相继被召。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1158')\">1158年2月</a>，二月壬子，垂拱殿奏事毕，极陈父冤。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1158')\">1158年</a>，除起居舍人。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1158')\">1158年</a>，撰《迩英记注》。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1158')\">1158年3月</a>，三月戊子奏对，为父乞谥。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1158')\">1158年6月</a>，六月甲辰作忠宣公谥告碑记。题衔称左朝散郎起居舍人。<span class='label'>作品：</span>忠宣公谥告碑记。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-450页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1158')\">1158年</a>，奏论张子正、子颜除官。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏论张子正、子颜除官。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-451页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1158')\">1158年</a>，经筵进褚遂良论漆器故事、又进汉文帝不凿露台故事，又进宋璟献《尚书·无逸》为图故事，又进韩昭侯敝绔故事。<span class='label'>作品：</span>经筵进褚遂良论漆器故事、又进汉文帝不凿露台故事，又进宋璟献《尚书·无逸》为图故事，又进韩昭侯敝绔故事。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-452页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1158')\">1158年7月</a>，七月戊寅，面对，论铸钱利害。帝嘉之，除起居郎兼枢密院都承旨。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1158')\">1158年</a>，请修绍兴九年以后起居注。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1158')\">1158年</a>，经筵进仁宗诏阁门通进银台司登闻检鼓院故事。<span class='label'>作品：</span>经筵进仁宗诏阁门通进银台司登闻检鼓院故事。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-455页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1158')\">1158年</a>，奏乞减免平江、湖、秀三州秋苗。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1158&endYear=1158')\">1158年</a>，兼权中书舍人。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年</a>，拜中书舍人。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年</a>，奏皇太后庆八十增恩数。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年</a>，论辅逵王纲转官。<span class='label'>作品：</span>论辅逵王纲转官。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-460页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年</a>，时勋臣子孙多躐居台省，奏乞明示禁止。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年</a>，与给事中王晞亮同上奏言，历任六考举官五员当如旧制。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年</a>，经筵进周世宗斩樊爱能等故事。<span class='label'>作品：</span>经筵进周世宗斩樊爱能等故事。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-463页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年</a>，论限田利弊。<span class='label'>作品：</span>论限田利弊。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-464页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年</a>，论李文会恤典。<span class='label'>作品：</span>论李文会恤典。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-465页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年</a>，奏请看详被赦罪人军伍。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏请看详被赦罪人军伍。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-466页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年</a>，缴罗殿蕃进马指挥并上奏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年</a>，奏乞榜谕瑞昌兴国失业茶商。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年</a>，论买马博易。<span class='label'>作品：</span>论买马博易。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-469页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年</a>，论祷雨思所当戒。<span class='label'>作品：</span>论祷雨思所当戒。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-470页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1159&endYear=1159')\">1159年</a>，论鄱阳永平、永丰两监宜复置鼓铸使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1160&endYear=1160')\">1160年1月</a>，正月乙酉，以中书舍人兼权尚书礼部侍郎。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1160&endYear=1160')\">1160年1月</a>，正月丁未，试吏部侍郎。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1160&endYear=1160')\">1160年</a>，奏荐王珏、林珦、胡梿。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏荐王珏、林珦、胡梿。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-474页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1160&endYear=1160')\">1160年</a>，奏革选人贿吏等弊。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1160&endYear=1160')\">1160年</a>，奏选举二事。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏选举二事。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-476页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1160&endYear=1160')\">1160年</a>，奏乞修国朝续会要。奏乞修国朝续会要。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1160&endYear=1160')\">1160年8月</a>，以吏部侍郎除翰林学士兼吏部尚书。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1160&endYear=1160')\">1160年</a>，奏论川陕淮汉立功将士当亟行赏。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏论川陕淮汉立功将士当亟行赏。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-479页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1160&endYear=1160')\">1160年9月</a>，诏试馆职，发策。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1160&endYear=1160')\">1160年</a>，汤思退罢相，当制。为汪澈所论，丐去。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1160&endYear=1160')\">1160年12月</a>，除徽猷阁直学士提举江太平兴国宫。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"dca0e00cf36f4db389d381c904cc32bf\");'><span id='dca0e00cf36f4db389d381c904cc32bf_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1162&endYear=1164')\">1162-1164年</a>，42-44岁</div><div id='dca0e00cf36f4db389d381c904cc32bf' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1162&endYear=1162')\">1162年5月</a>，以徽猷阁直学士知平江府除翰林学士。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1162&endYear=1162')\">1162年6月</a>，孝宗即位，除承旨兼侍读。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1162&endYear=1162')\">1162年</a>，撰禅位诏、登极赦文、尊号、改元等文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>禅位诏、登极赦文、尊号、改元等文。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-488页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1162&endYear=1162')\">1162年</a>，奏请申敕中外循太上皇后之训。<span class='label'>作品：</span>奏请申敕中外循太上皇后之训。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-489页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1162&endYear=1162')\">1162年</a>，有诏议应敌定论，与金安节等相继论列。<span class='label'>作品：</span>制敌定计劄子。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-490页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1162&endYear=1162')\">1162年</a>，奏乞放免昆山县隐户田赋。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞放免昆山县隐户田赋劄子。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-491页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1162&endYear=1162')\">1162年</a>，奏荐张允之、郭沰、吴松年、张晙。<span class='label'>作品：</span>举监司郡守劄子。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-492页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1163&endYear=1163')\">1163年1月</a>，礼部试进士，为知贡举。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1163&endYear=1163')\">1163年</a>，撰《中兴以来玉堂制草》。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1163&endYear=1163')\">1163年5月</a>，丁未，自翰林学士承旨知制诰兼侍读迁左中大夫同知枢密院事。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1163&endYear=1163')\">1163年5月</a>，金人陷宿州，与计议官卢仲贤遗金帅纥石烈志宁书。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1164&endYear=1164')\">1164年</a>，寿康殿产芝，同列议表贺，遵风止之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1164&endYear=1164')\">1164年</a>，奏荐眉山李焘、永嘉郑伯熊及林光朝。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1164&endYear=1164')\">1164年</a>，御史周璪论遵，遵连章乞罢。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1164&endYear=1164')\">1164年7月</a>，丁亥，罢同知，以端明殿学士提举太平兴国宫。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1164&endYear=1164')\">1164年7月</a>，庚戌，落端明殿学士。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"8be621cf04ab46c4901682345c7307c3\");'><span id='8be621cf04ab46c4901682345c7307c3_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1173&endYear=1173')\">1173年</a>，53岁</div><div id='8be621cf04ab46c4901682345c7307c3' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1173&endYear=1173')\">1173年12月27日</a>，以资政殿学士提举临安府洞霄宫。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.816791,"Longitude":119.980142,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3204",