<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.036519,"Longitude":120.586673,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3306","Title":"绍兴","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e3f2206387d448578de2aac8b63d2c66\");'><span id='e3f2206387d448578de2aac8b63d2c66_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1155&endYear=1155')\">1155年</a>，35岁</div><div id='e3f2206387d448578de2aac8b63d2c66' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1155&endYear=1155')\">1155年</a>，通判越州。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.304566,"Longitude":120.589613,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3205","Title":"苏州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"a996b7ecd68b4cd6aa0fdd7b0830faa0\");'><span id='a996b7ecd68b4cd6aa0fdd7b0830faa0_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1161&endYear=1161')\">1161年</a>，41岁</div><div id='a996b7ecd68b4cd6aa0fdd7b0830faa0' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1161&endYear=1161')\">1161年</a>，知平江府。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1161&endYear=1161')\">1161年</a>，乞精选间谍。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞精选间谍。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-484页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1161&endYear=1161')\">1161年12月</a>，车驾至平江，因对，论商船事。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":28.968047,"Longitude":117.135438,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN360281","Title":"乐平","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"8952606b984b4912bd1cdb07d02d7506\");'><span id='8952606b984b4912bd1cdb07d02d7506_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1165&endYear=1169')\">1165-1169年</a>，45-49岁</div><div id='8952606b984b4912bd1cdb07d02d7506' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1165&endYear=1165')\">1165年</a>，居乡。作《滃潭隧表》。<span class='label'>作品：</span>滃潭隧表。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-502页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1166&endYear=1166')\">1166年</a>，居乡。作小隐园。因以小隐自号。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1167&endYear=1169')\">1167-1169年</a>，居乡。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"772a831d587c4335ac615d0a3e883d9e\");'><span id='772a831d587c4335ac615d0a3e883d9e_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1174&endYear=1174')\">1174年</a>，54岁</div><div id='772a831d587c4335ac615d0a3e883d9e' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1174&endYear=1174')\">1174年</a>，归鄱阳乡居。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1174&endYear=1174')\">1174年11月</a>，薨。晋少保，封信国公，谥文安。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":28.460864,"Longitude":117.950028,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3611","Title":"上饶","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"438beb5427fb464789ce9c6561e2636b\");'><span id='438beb5427fb464789ce9c6561e2636b_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1170&endYear=1170')\">1170年</a>，50岁</div><div id='438beb5427fb464789ce9c6561e2636b' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1170&endYear=1170')\">1170年</a>，起知信州。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":31.358798,"Longitude":118.439561,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3402","Title":"芜湖","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"0bcfe0965a98419c9c2bc728f450e1be\");'><span id='0bcfe0965a98419c9c2bc728f450e1be_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1170&endYear=1170')\">1170年</a>，50岁</div><div id='0bcfe0965a98419c9c2bc728f450e1be' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1170&endYear=1170')\">1170年</a>，徙知太平州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1170&endYear=1170')\">1170年</a>，圩田坏，鸠民筑之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1170&endYear=1170')\">1170年</a>，罢苗米输耗，听民自持斛概。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1170&endYear=1170')\">1170年</a>，岁大饥，有乞借江西米劄子。蠲租账赡活者万计。戍兵为盗，拘执归军。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞借江西米劄子。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-511页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1170&endYear=1170')\">1170年</a>，有乞存留拣中禁军劄子。<span class='label'>作品：</span>乞存留拣中禁军劄子。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-512页。）</span><br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.064735,"Longitude":118.802891,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3201","Title":"南京","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"5a1a3b369a164ad7bde2a78ebb102951\");'><span id='5a1a3b369a164ad7bde2a78ebb102951_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1171&endYear=1173')\">1171-1173年</a>，51-53岁</div><div id='5a1a3b369a164ad7bde2a78ebb102951' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1171&endYear=1171')\">1171年</a>，徙知建康府、江东安抚使兼行营留守。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1171&endYear=1171')\">1171年7月</a>，入觐赴选德殿奏事，进资政殿学士。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1171&endYear=1171')\">1171年</a>，奏荐邵宏渊。<span class='label'>作品：</span>荐邵宏渊。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-515页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1171&endYear=1171')\">1171年</a>，荐赵撙、郭刚。<span class='label'>作品：</span>荐赵撙、郭刚。<span class='inlineComment2'>（北京图书馆藏珍本年谱丛刊第25册，第333-516页。）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1171&endYear=1171')\">1171年</a>，荐梁公永、程渭老。<span class='label'>作品：</span>荐梁公永、程渭老。<s